      "created": "2014-12-10T15:20:29.173+0000",
      "description": "For YARN clients to make effective use of this, we need an equivalent service {{YarnClientImpl}}. The closer the REST client to this existing class (and the {{YarnClient}} API, the easier the migration.\n\nRequirements of SLIDER-170\n\nNeeds\n* work long-haul, through proxies and security gateways like Apache Knox\n* Integration with Hadoop security\n* diagnostics and meaningful error messages\n* ability interrupt outstanding calls\n\nWants\n* ideally some performance metrics to track  long-haul perf issues (prefer codahale to Hadoop, for embeddability)\n* tunable restart/retry policy",
